✨Over the years, Lake Las Vegas has become a popular destination for events and festivals. The area hosts a range of outdoor concerts, art shows, and community gatherings throughout the year. These events enhance the community’s vibrant atmosphere, providing opportunities for residents and visitors to come together and revel in the surroundings. Lake Las Vegas offers a unique fusion of natural beauty, upscale living, and recreational activities. Serving as an oasis in the desert, it provides a tranquil escape for those seeking a distinct experience away from the world-famous Las Vegas Strip.

William Brauner, the owner of Luxury Homes of Las Vegas, began his Las Vegas career in Lake Las Vegas several decades ago and developed a profound affection for the area.

✨Owner Spotlight✨
As a third-generation Las Vegas resident, Tyler Brady is a Broker | Owner with an exceptional commitment to helping you add to your own Las Vegas legacy. With experience not only as an agent but also as a broker, Tyler understands luxury real estate and the importance of providing clients with a customized concierge experience. Dedicated and passionate, Tyler focuses on ensuring his personalized and professional approach will result in a smooth buying or selling process - whether for a first-time homebuyer or a real estate pro.

Before joining Luxury Homes of Las Vegas, Tyler was the Owner and Broker for Brady Luxury Collection, a distinguished real estate brokerage and luxury sales arm of Brady Realty Group. Tyler's experience before real estate was varied, ranging from Sales at Brady Industries and Brady Linen, a national jan-san distribution and commercial laundry company, to working in Music Management for ROX Management, Aware Records, a subsidiary of Columbia Records, along with independent A&R for Capital Records and Atlantic Records. #lasvegas #luxuryhomes #luxuryhomeslasvegas
